bjfu-shortcuts
==============

"I used to marvel at their powful tools, now I decide to steal their creativity
and make my own toys"
                                      --The reason why I made bjfu-shortcuts

bjfu-wifi auto login
--------------------

The bjfu-shortcuts includes severl iOS shortcuts, tends to simplify 
snippy Web Authentication API to login bjfu-wifi. Due to the different 
frontend of bjfu-wifi, the different area of school is equipped with 
its own POST head to login bjfu-wifi. With these "historical" network 
situation, bjfu-shortcuts now introducing multiple, specific shortcuts 
scripts to login bjfu-wifi. Here's finished bjfu-shortcuts to login bjfu-wifi:

for dorm bjfu-wifi auto login:

    https://www.icloud.com/shortcuts/a8402bae05e441f0ae00030a8e13103f

for library(haven't confirmed) and lab bjfu-wifi auto login:

    https://www.icloud.com/shortcuts/de55bf9fb78d418f99e7ddffe59c7972
    
other area wifi login haven't been developed, waitting for update


bjfu information check
----------------------

The information check shortcuts will be introducing soon(or never), including 
grades points / course / notification / offical info, etc


